# Porch Petals Environment Variables

# Stripe Configuration
VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your_stripe_publishable_key_here

# Notion Integration (optional - will use mock data if not provided)
VITE_NOTION_TOKEN=secret_your_notion_integration_token_here
VITE_NOTION_DATABASE_ID=your_notion_database_id_here

# Example Notion Database Structure:
# Your Notion database should have these properties:
# - Name (Title) - The bouquet name
# - Available (Number) - Current available count
# - Total (Number) - Total capacity for this bouquet type
# 
# Example rows:
# | Name           | Available | Total |
# |----------------|-----------|-------|
# | Minnie Zinnie  | 3         | 5     |
# | Garden Mix     | 2         | 3     |
# | Sunshine Bundle| 1         | 2     |